description-of-drawings.p: FIG. 1 is a first perspective view of a receiver for dog training collar showing the claimed design in accordance with the present disclosure;
FIG. 2 is a second perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a front elevational view thereof;
FIG. 4 is a rear elevational view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a left side elevational view thereof;

claim.claim-text: The ornamental design for a receiver for dog training collar, as shown and described.
